    <entry>
      <title>Certbot 申请证书以及续费</title>
      <link href="/posts/certbot/"/>
      <url>/posts/certbot/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装过程跳过</p><h1 id="申请证书"><a href="#申请证书" class="headerlink" title="申请证书"></a>申请证书</h1><p>通过DNS验证域名：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">certbot certonly -d *.yokinanya.icu --manual --preferred-challenges dns</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按照提示在域名服务商处，添加对应的DNS TXT解析记录。<br>配置好后按回车继续，如果是修改记录的话，建议等一个TTL的时间再按回车</p><h1 id="续费"><a href="#续费" class="headerlink" title="续费"></a>续费</h1><p>自动续费：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">certbot renew</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以设置个定时任务：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 1 */1 * * certbot renew &gt; /var/log/crontab/certbot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>后面日志文件路径随便改，前面定时也可以随便改</p><p>强制重签:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">certbot certonly --manual -d *.yokinanya.icu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Minecraft Fabric 生电向整合包</title>
      <link href="/posts/minecraft-modpacket/"/>
      <url>/posts/minecraft-modpacket/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h1><p>这是一个Minecraft整合包合集页面，包含从1.18.2起由我打包的各类整合包，以生电向mod为主<br/><br>整合包一般都会包含以下mod，无特殊情况不再重复描述：</p><details> <summary> 展开mod列表 </summary><table><thead><tr><th>mod名称</th><th>下载地址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>AppleSkin</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/appleskin">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/EsAfCjCV">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Architectury</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/architectury-api">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/lhGA9TYQ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Auth Me</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/auth-me">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/yjgIrBjZ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>AutoFish</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/autofish">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>Bad Packets</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/badpackets">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/ftdbN0KK">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Better Beds</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-beds">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/kKwy3HU9">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>CIT Resewn</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cit-resewn">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/otVJckYQ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet Mod</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/TQTTVgYE">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet Extra</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet-extra">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/VX3TgwQh">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet TCTC Addition</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet-tctc-addition">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/vbBQ6dVH">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet TIS Addition</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet-tis-addition">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/jE0SjGuf">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Chat Heads</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chat-heads">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/Wb5oqrBJ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Cloth Config API</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cloth-config">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/9s6osm5g">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Continuity</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/continuity">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/1IjD5062">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>CustomSkinLoader</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/customskinloader">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>Enhanced Block Entities</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enhanced-block-entities">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/OVuFYfre">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Fabric Api</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/P7dR8mSH">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Fabric Language Kotlin</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-language-kotlin">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/Ha28R6CL">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>FerriteCore</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ferritecore-fabric">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/uXXizFIs">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>IMBlocker</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/imblockerfabric">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/752GQt04">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Indium</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/indium">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/Orvt0mRa">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Inventory Profiles Next</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/inventory-profiles-next">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/O7RBXm3n">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Iris Shaders</td><td><a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/YL57xq9U">Modrinth</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://irisshaders.dev/download">官网</a></td></tr><tr><td>Item Scroller</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/item-scroller">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>Litematica</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/litematica">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>MaLiLib</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/malilib">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>MagicLib</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/magiclib">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/mv1zH6ln">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Masa Gadget</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/masa-gadget">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/SFO4Ca80">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>MiniHUD</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/minihud">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>Mod Menu</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/modmenu">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/mOgUt4GM">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>More Statistics</td><td><a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/EhoUIqvO">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>oh my minecraft client</td><td><a href="https://github.com/Nyan-Work/oh-my-minecraft-client">Github</a></td></tr><tr><td>Plusls Carpet Addition</td><td><a href="https://github.com/Nyan-Work/plusls-carpet-addition">Github</a></td></tr><tr><td>Reese’s Sodium Options</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/reeses-sodium-options">Curseforge</a> <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/Bh37bMuy">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Roughly Enough Items</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/roughly-enough-items">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/nfn13YXA">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Screenshot to Clipboard</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/screenshot-to-clipboard-fabric">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/1KiJRrTg">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Sodium</td><td><a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/AANobbMI">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Sodium Extra</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/sodium-extra">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/PtjYWJkn">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Starlight</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/starlight">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/H8CaAYZC">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>TweakerMore</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/tweakermore">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/GBeCx05I">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Tweakeroo</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/tweakeroo">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>TweakMyClient</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/tweakmyclient">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>Xaero’s Minimap</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/xaeros-minimap">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/1bokaNcj">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Xaero’s World Map</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/xaeros-world-map">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/NcUtCpym">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>libIPN</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/libipn">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/libipn">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>spark</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/spark">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/l6YH9Als">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>WTHIT</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/wthit">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/6AQIaxuO">Modrinth</a></td></tr></tbody></table></details><p><br/>1.20.1 起追加mod</p><p><a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/G1epq3jN">AdvancementInfo</a><br><a href="https://github.com/charassss/tin3o">TIN3O</a><br><a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/pGbwwB5d">LetMeClickAndSend</a></p><h1 id="1-18-2-Vanilla"><a href="#1-18-2-Vanilla" class="headerlink" title="1.18.2 Vanilla"></a>1.18.2 Vanilla</h1><blockquote><p>整合包为原版分支<br>更新日期：2023-07-06</p></blockquote><p>此版本使用了 <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/K8pn1qHf">OAuth</a> 替代了 Auth Me</p><h1 id="1-18-2-Create"><a href="#1-18-2-Create" class="headerlink" title="1.18.2 Create"></a>1.18.2 Create</h1><blockquote><p>整合包为机械动力分支<br>更新日期：2023-07-06</p></blockquote><p>在 1.18.2 Vanilla 的基础上增加了 <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric">机械动力</a>、<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/4EakbH8e">农夫乐事</a>、<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/5aaWibi9">Trinkets</a>及其附属mod<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/b5GyyYkp">不死图腾插槽</a> <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/mSQF1NpT">鞘翅插槽</a></p><h1 id="1-19-4"><a href="#1-19-4" class="headerlink" title="1.19.4"></a>1.19.4</h1><blockquote><p>整合包为原版分支<br>发布日期：2023-04-04</p></blockquote><p>整合包有部分mod是我自行添加汉化文件的，1.19.4整合包不存在机械动力分支</p><h1 id="1-20-1-Vanilla"><a href="#1-20-1-Vanilla" class="headerlink" title="1.20.1 Vanilla"></a>1.20.1 Vanilla</h1><blockquote><p>整合包为原版分支<br>发布日期：2023-08-23</p></blockquote><p>整合包有部分mod使用了第三方分支版本</p><h1 id="1-20-1-Create"><a href="#1-20-1-Create" class="headerlink" title="1.20.1 Create"></a>1.20.1 Create</h1><blockquote><p>整合包为机械动力分支<br>发布日期：2023-08-25</p></blockquote><p>在 1.20.1 Vanilla 的基础上增加了 <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric">机械动力</a>、<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/4EakbH8e">农夫乐事</a>、<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/5aaWibi9">Trinkets</a>及其附属mod<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/b5GyyYkp">不死图腾插槽</a> <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/mSQF1NpT">鞘翅插槽</a></p><p>已知bug：</p><ul><li>实体方块在Sodium 5.0下无法正常显示 <a href="https://github.com/Fabricators-of-Create/Create/issues/1039">#1039</a></li><li>与starlight冲突会导致游戏崩溃 <a href="https://github.com/Fabricators-of-Create/Create/issues/1041">#1041</a></li></ul><p>临时解决方案：</p><ul><li>暂时使用Sodium 4.0版本</li><li>删除整合包内starlight</li></ul><h1 id="启动器"><a href="#启动器" class="headerlink" title="启动器"></a>启动器</h1><p>整合包内可能没有附带启动器，或者附带了jar格式的HMCL启动器，用Linux&#x2F;MacOS的应该熟悉，在Windows下如果正确配置了环境变量是可以直接双击运行的。如果需要.exe格式的HMLC启动器可以前往<a href="https://hmcl.huangyuhui.net/">HMCL官网</a>下载。或者你想用PCL2、BakaXL，可以把游戏目录自行添加到对应启动器内。<br><strong>注意：不是导入整合包，而是添加已有文件夹</strong></p><h1 id="光影"><a href="#光影" class="headerlink" title="光影"></a>光影</h1><p>所有整合包均不会使用Optifine，使用光影需要注意光影是否有适配Iris</p><h1 id="第一次启动"><a href="#第一次启动" class="headerlink" title="第一次启动"></a>第一次启动</h1><p>游戏第一次启动需要联网下载游戏资源文件，如果需要在离线环境下游玩，需要提前在一台联网的电脑下载资源文件再复制到离线的电脑上。</p><h1 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h1><table><thead><tr><th>下载源</th><th>文件服务器</th><th>大陆&#x2F;海外</th><th>正式版</th><th>预览版</th><th>客户端</th><th>服务器端</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href="https://share.weiyun.com/PT0hKNFW">腾讯微云</a>(提取码：7e9ure)</td><td>腾讯云</td><td>大陆</td><td>✓</td><td>×</td><td>√</td><td>×</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=FpNvPiwKEBbBRHMvH8-M6Kp1WTB8L6W0">QQ群</a>(1067555292)</td><td>腾讯云COS</td><td>大陆</td><td>✓</td><td>√</td><td>√</td><td>√</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://drivez.yokinanya.icu/Minecraft">绫沫猫猫冲下载站</a></td><td>Onedrive国际版</td><td>海外</td><td>✓</td><td>√</td><td>√</td><td>X</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
      
